                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-744-18560818 t18560818-744-punishment-22"></join>Confined Nine Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">PAVELEY</hi>—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18560818-744-punishment-23" type="punishmentDescription">
